# Permutation of all forms of construction
# when fusing a box and a prism
box ba 3 3 0 5 7 4

# prism from left

vertex v1 3 3 4
vertex v2 3 4 4
vertex v3 3 4 5
vertex v4 3 3 5

edge ea v1 v2
edge eb v2 v3
edge ec v3 v4
edge ed v4 v1

wire w ea eb ec ed
mkplane f w

prism bb f 1 0 0

bfuse result ba bb

checkprops result -s 170
checkview -display result -2d -otherwise { ba bb } -s -path ${imagedir}/${test_image}.png